These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: coffee, fanta
Movie-Genre: crime, spy
Sport: cycling, surfing
Nationality: dutch, mexican
1. Nationality:mexican is on the left or right of Sport:surfing##3
2. Beverage:fanta is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:spy == Beverage:coffee##1
4. Nationality:mexican is on the right of Nationality:dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | crime   |
| Sport         | surfing | cycling |
| Nationality     | dutch | mexican    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
Food: avocado, cabbage
House: colonial, townhouse
Pet: dog, rat
Transport: motorbike, tram
1. Pet:rat is in an odd position##4
2. House:colonial == Transport:tram##1
3. Food:cabbage is on the right of House:townhouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | avocado     | cabbage |
| House   | townhouse | colonial  |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| Transport     | motorbike   | tram    |

 #################################
 
